Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄关的门要关好啊  真是不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  洗发水用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.57,0:00:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵…喵
