Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:44.29,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Be Starters！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:49.71,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}充满未知数的门扉  也要毫无畏惧地去开启
